            <p facs="#facs_19_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>-488-
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>This means, further, that theontical element, which partly comes from the collegues
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>and the public discussion about research, also comes from the immediate encounter with the
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>students. And I wouldn't believe that I would know anything about anything without this
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>critical raction, this wall which must be pierced each time when you get here to the desk,
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>[pierced] in terms of giving conviction, and very often you don’t succed, and then what is
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_3_tl_7" n="N007"/>said comes back from the wall which you were not able to which through. Now that's the
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_19_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>great importance of the combination of teachingandaren¬
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>In the Nesearch, the vdecisive principle is truth. But truth has several levels. There
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>are three levels--and I had a case just last Tuesday, in a group ofnenlars, collleagues of
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>different
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>Faculties, mostly of the natural science, to discuss the different level of truth with
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>the
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>them. In the introduction for this discussion, I distinguished the truth in the realm of the
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>subject-object experience,ossalyzing the objects as a subject, and.handling them in terms of
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>technical dealing with them. This is the one realm, which one could call, following Max Scheler
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>in this, "controlling knowledge," knowledge of control. Then the second, following Plato
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>in this respect, one could speak of Grarticipation in realities which cannot be known in terms of
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>anelysis and control but in terms of Grarticipation and eros, as Plato called it, namely the other
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>personality, the realms of the good and the beautiful, the intuition of those qualities of being which
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_1_tl_14" n="N014"/>are not objects of analysis, calculation and Engagement.
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_19_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>Then the third level, existential truth, namely the truth in which we commit ourselves
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>dire une
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>de mon ami
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>by the
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>Monsieur,
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>cʼest avec
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>dʼune manière est
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_11" n="N011"/>dans le
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_12" n="N012"/>toutes
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_13" n="N013"/>G.C.P.
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_14" n="N014"/>dans un autre
               <lb facs="#facs_19_tr_2_tl_15" n="N015"/>dire une
